    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Texts by artists, often brief, that state, for example, explanations of the artists' work or theoretical concepts on which their work is based.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
